Package: rmRNAseq
Type: Package
Title: RNA-seq Analysis for Repeated-measures Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yet Nguyen <tienyettoan@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Yet Nguyen <tienyettoan@gmail.com>
Description: This package implement parametric bootstrap inference method to identify differentially expressed genes using RNA-seq data. The method is using voom-limma differential expression analysis method.
Depends: R (>= 3.3)
